               <h2 class="tjust"><a href="">Our guiding principle</a></h2>

            <div class="articletext">
                 <div class="articlesummary">
                     <p class="nobottommargin">We believe that change in business is not an occasional event, it is a daily event; and the most successful businesses, in any industry, demonstrate an ability to measure, analyze and nimbly adapt their Business Processes to capitalize on rather than  react to change. <br/><br/>
                     This is the cornerstone of our Business Process Management Consulting. Samuels Consulting brings strategic to tactical expertise in Business Process analysis and design, the use of existing Technology for management data and efficiency and the optimization of Human Resources in the Business Process.</p>

                     <span class="articlemore">
                       <!-- <a href="wwcd4yb.html" title="more... What we can do for your Business"><img src="img/SamuelsConsulting_Logo_150x150.jpg" alt="" width="20" height="20" />learn more...</a> -->
                     </span>
