                  <a href="">What we can do for your business</a></h2>

            <div class="articletext">
                 <div class="articlesummary">
                     <p class="nobottommargin">Analyze, Align and Optimize your Business Processes to improve product/service accuracy, timeliness and control; resulting in an increase in shareholder value, improved utilization of your human resources and improved customer satisfaction.</p>

                     <span class="articlemore">
