               <h2 class="tjust"><a href="">Typical deliverables of a BPM project:</a></h2>

            <div class="articletext">
                 <div class="articlesummary">
                     <ul class="pbott">
<li>Review and analysis of the current protocols, workflows and human resource skills/needs</li>
<li>Scalable recommendations for BP re-design/design directly tied to results</li>
<li>Functional organization to ensure authority/accountability in key BP managers</li>
<li>Use of technology for efficiency, daily BP management and reporting metrics</li>
<li>Alignment of human resource skills with the BP needs</li>
<li>Establish on-going review and management processes to anticipate and address business risks/opportunities</li>
</ul>
